wiki.content: Produced by Mutt Lange. Featuring Queen's Brian May on guitar. The You and I Songfacts states that Gaga finds it hard to perform this track as it is about her relationship with her on-and-off boyfriend, Luc Carl. The tune is about getting back together with a former love and Gaga penned the tune after getting back together with Carl, having previously split up with him. However, the singer broke up with him again shortly before the release of Born This Way and she now gets upset when singing the tune.
